			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    High Elf Oracle</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=2785"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:Rangers_84@hotmail.com">Infirit</a> | 
		                        1/5/2000 6:40:23 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">In the Ocean of Tears near the sisters of Erossili island there is a gigh elf and a guard. The Oracle states that he wants to become the master of knowledge and asks you to find 7 or 8 books to give him. since i have not yet completed this quest i dont know if its worth it but i believe one of the books is Tergons book gotten from a Orc Prophet.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
