				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If you take the Oracle out, yes, you do get the robe.  But, no your level 25 mage isn't going to be enough, sorry.  You see, the oracle is about level 30 or so and he's not even your biggest worry.  The guard who stands next to him is about level 40 or so.  You need a couple of friends to help you out.  Preferrably your level or higher, you need someone who can root that guard and you need someone who can snare that oracle.  I used my level 30 cleric to cast snare and wrath and I had 3 friends help me snare him, and lull the guard.  All my friends were higher level than me and it still took us about 30 seconds of strong blasting to kill him.  He has alot of HP for a single NPC.  No way I would have had enough mana to do all the work myself and my wis was 186.  Good luck.
